                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Report of the Deputies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council heard and approved the Deputies’ Report.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Italo-Yugoslav Frontier and Trieste</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Ministers exchanged views on this question. All Delegations expressed the
                    view that the whole territory to the east of the line proposed by the French
                    Delegation should be ceded to Yugoslavia.</p>
                <p>It was agreed to continue the discussion of this question at the Council’s next
                    meeting.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Tuesday, 2nd July, at 4 p.m.</p>
